snippet.title: Blackberry Honey 【Original Song】
snippet.description:
The intro movie for Blackberry Honey, a yuri visual novel by ebihime!

🍯 Available on Steam now: http://store.steampowered.com/app/716340/Blackberry_Honey/
🍯 Bandcamp: https://yuzuki.bandcamp.com/album/blackberry-honey
🍯 Itch.io: Soon

Vocals: Saki (https://twitter.com/sakiseshy)
Lyrics: Geiky (https://twitter.com/geikroitz)
Art: Oxykoma (https://twitter.com/Oxykoma)
Music: yuzuki (https://twitter.com/yuzukimasu)
Video: Kusa (https://twitter.com/haipeww)
Master: Ranzor (https://soundcloud.com/ranzor)
